    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space Engineers – 简体中文本地化版本</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space Engineers 是一款硬核 Sandbox 工程建造 游戏。你可以在一个“完全可破坏”的宇宙中设计、建造各种飞船、空间站与星球基地。探索行星与太空、挖矿采集、躲避危险，还能在 Creative 或 Survival 模式中，与朋友一起作战或独自生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space Engineers 是一款开放世界 Sandbox 游戏，核心就是设计、建造、测试你自己的太空机械。你可以在完全可破坏的环境中打造飞船、空间站与行星基地，然后前往宇宙深处探索、采矿、求生、战斗——支持单人，也支持多人合作/对抗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以独自游戏，也可以加入多人联机，从三五好友的小据点到社区运营的大型服务器都没问题。你可以从一艘简易的着陆器起步，慢慢发展成庞大的采矿工业帝国；也可以专注打造战舰或行星要塞。工具和物理系统都给你了——造什么由你决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用“体积物理引擎”：每一个方块、每一个体素都有质量、惯性和损伤判定。飞船会被打碎、基地会崩塌，地形可以被钻孔、切削、炸开并重新塑形——每一个工程决策都真实影响结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space Engineers 的一切都基于真实工程与硬科幻逻辑，强调真实感和“近未来可实现”的技术路线。可以把它想象成把现代航天工程往前推进几十年：飞船、空间站、工具与系统全部“按块模拟”，没有魔法，也没有预设剧情，只靠你亲手打造的机械系统驱动游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/244850/extras/3f4e8b563d04308f5eec1102ee99061c.poster.avif?t=1768927358\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/244850/extras/3f4e8b563d04308f5eec1102ee99061c.webm?t=1768927358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/244850/extras/3f4e8b563d04308f5eec1102ee99061c.mp4?t=1768927358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为什么现在玩 Space Engineers（SE1）？</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >连续 10+ 年的持续开发，每年都有大量免费更新（并且还在继续）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam 创意工坊拥有数千个玩家作品：飞船、基地、Mod、脚本和剧情</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >稳定、成熟、功能齐全的 Sandbox，适合长期存档与大型服务器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DLC 全部是纯外观——核心玩法人人一致</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家群体活跃，专用服务器和 Mod 社区长期在线</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/244850/extras/baa344fa24216040e38f85818f272b59.poster.avif?t=1768927358\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/244850/extras/baa344fa24216040e38f85818f272b59.webm?t=1768927358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/244850/extras/baa344fa24216040e38f85818f272b59.mp4?t=1768927358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心玩法特点</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随心建造</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设计并驾驶大小飞船、空间站与行星基地</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过 200 种功能方块：推进器、转子、活塞、炮塔、传送管线、生产方块等等</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持第一/第三人称建造、对称工具、Blueprint 蓝图批量建造</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival 模式中依靠手动焊接/打磨来组装与拆解组件</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >完全可破坏世界</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体素行星、卫星与小行星，拥有大气、重力与气候区域</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地形可被钻、切、爆炸处理；可以挖隧道、挖陨坑、建地底基地</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >船体与建筑会受到逐块损伤，可被击碎成残骸</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有物体都有真实质量、储存空间和结构完整度</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/244850/extras/c5d838d7661440dea5169459de54268d.poster.avif?t=1768927358\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/244850/extras/c5d838d7661440dea5169459de54268d.webm?t=1768927358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/244850/extras/c5d838d7661440dea5169459de54268d.mp4?t=1768927358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >想怎么玩就怎么玩</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creative 创造模式：无限资源、瞬时建造、不会死亡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival 生存模式：手动组装、资源/能源管理、死亡与重生</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持单人、合作、对抗，多人服务器可设私密性与权限</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种官方/玩家自制的世界、剧本，让你选择喜欢的开局方式</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/244850/extras/5ecd3ecb4a8f23df19b355b3a72d3612.poster.avif?t=1768927358\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/244850/extras/5ecd3ecb4a8f23df19b355b3a72d3612.webm?t=1768927358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/244850/extras/5ecd3ecb4a8f23df19b355b3a72d3612.mp4?t=1768927358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可重复游玩性极高</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超大规模宇宙，搭配程序生成的小行星与探索事件</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索系统会生成可发现、可劫持、可征服的飞船与空间站</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内置可视化脚本编辑器，制作自己的任务、模式和战役</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AI 派系、货船巡逻队和敌对威胁随时等你互动或反击</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Modding &amp; 脚本</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深度整合 Steam 创意工坊，支持世界、蓝图、Mod、脚本等多种内容</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提供 C# Modding API，可自定义游戏行为与系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Programmable Block 可在游戏内编写自动化与逻辑控制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持自定义材质、模型和大量 Mod 类型</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/244850/extras/baa344fa24216040e38f85818f272b59.poster.avif?t=1768927358\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/244850/extras/baa344fa24216040e38f85818f272b59.webm?t=1768927358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/244850/extras/baa344fa24216040e38f85818f272b59.mp4?t=1768927358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >系统 &amp; 生存机制</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >电力系统、电网与发电机管理整座基地或整艘飞船</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >氧气与氢气用于生命维持与推进器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种武器方块用于太空战斗与地面防御</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GPS、远程操控、Voxel Hands、手柄支持等大量便利功能</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多语言支持丰富，包含官方与社区翻译</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
